content:
Great choice with the Portobello Mushroom Burger! It’s a delicious option, but just to clarify, it does come with regular cheese unless you add a vegan cheese option. Yes, we do have vegan cheese available for an extra $2.50.

And yes, it can come with sweet potato fries! Would you like to have that as your side? Also, do you want the vegan cheese on your burger?
